  "texts": [
    "If the case survives dismissal, the next step is for the plaintiffs to request class certification by the judge.",
    "The general requirements for class certification are: 1.",
    "\"Commonality, meaning there are questions of law or fact common to the class\" (Practical Law Securities Litigation & White Collar Crime 2023); 2.",
    "\"Typicality, meaning that the claims or defenses of the named plaintiff are typical of the class\" (Practical Law Securities Litigation & White Collar Crime 2023); and 3.",
    "\"Adequacy, meaning that the named plaintiff must fairly and adequately protect the interests of the class\" (Practical Law Securities Litigation & White Collar Crime 2023)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}